Add or remove previously defined service from permanent or runtime config:
# firewall-cmd [--permanent] --add-service=<servicename>
# firewall-cmd [--permanent] --remove-service=<servicename>
Example:
   # firewall-cmd --permanent --add-service=http

Add or remove port from permanent or runtime config:
# firewall-cmd [--permanent] --add-port=<port>/<protocol>
# firewall-cmd [--permanent] --remove-port=<port>/<protocol>
